                <h2>Gargantuan News</h2>
                <p>Yep, my<strong> Gargantuan Book of Words&nbsp;</strong>is big&nbsp;&amp; full of words. Not just English but secret codes, Papuan pidgin, Zulu worms, sound FX, funny goldfish, letter origami. You get the drift? It's big. It's fun. And it's <a href="https://www.allenandunwin.com/browse/books/childrens/David-Astles-Gargantuan-Book-of-Words-David-Astle-9781760296223">out now</a>.&nbsp;</p>                <img src="/images/medal.png" width="28" height="54" alt="Medal" class="medal" />
              </div>
            </div>
          
